{"tid":2170131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飯民梁繼昌：民調具誤差　未必適宜作去留唯一依據","createTime":"2020-08-23T05:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T12:14:16.000Z","uid":73883,"like":2,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4223d3c3e6527320dfe8a44521852877c28690","tid":2170131,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"民主派立法會議員是否接受延任的問題，近日引起關注。會計界立法會議員梁繼昌在港台節目《給香港的信》中表示，明白到民意授權的重要性，也知道有論者質疑未來一年議會的合法性，但指民主派一向都在有限的空間內作盡可能的抗爭。他又擔心，民調受限於時間、資源和誤差等因素，是否適合單純按照民調決定最終去留。他又反思指，延任立法會若不合合法，2021年、2025年及以後的選舉是否都不應參與。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 支那01"},{"pid":"4146fdbd8ff76978faaf07ff093aeff48e8f1695","tid":2170131,"uid":285165,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"cls<br />\n真係林鄭咁 <br />\n咩都講得出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345f1805fa434df7084e989b6ef482777bb681c9","tid":2170131,"uid":158613,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:05:51.000Z","msg":"唔啱你心水姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7315f209a564c105339dc96810f42d70a9101b5c","tid":2170131,"uid":73883,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"延任係人大授權<br />\n2021 及 2025 選舉(如果有的話)係選民授權<br />\n要有幾智障先會信佢呢啲詭辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8897f429f8b2596a37c9249c1066a18de2daf74b","tid":2170131,"uid":3860,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7315f209a564c105339dc96810f42d70a9101b5c","tid":2170131,"uid":73883,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"延任係人大授權<br />\n2021 及 2025 選舉(如果有的話)係選民授權<br />\n要有幾智障先會信佢呢啲詭辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n打稻草